[gd_scene load_steps=18 format=3]

; Dev-only greybox for the task-10 manual playtest (F6). Not wired into GameManager — mission flow
; is task 11. Press "gadget_use" to trip a LOUD alarm and watch the PursuitDirector escalate phases
; (printed), Heat rise, and reinforcement requests log. Two armed guards patrol; walk into a cone to
; pull one into COMBAT — it keeps a standoff distance and shoots back (fire with "fire"). Damage
; routes through the player's Armor → Health → Downed → Caught. Direct steering, no nav-mesh bake.

